<p class="text"><strong>PAGE TEXT<br>
</strong>Customize the title and text for each page in an order site. 
Below are brief descriptions of the function of each page. [&nbsp;<a href="site-pagetext.php">More</a>&nbsp;]</p>
<p class="text"><strong>HOMEPAGE<br>
     </strong>Customize homepage text and graphics, set the homepage to 
  be the catalog, or use a custom page as the homepage. [ <a href="site-home.php">More</a>&nbsp;]</p>
<p class="text"><strong>CATALOG<br>
</strong><span class="text">Turn login for ordering off and on. Set catalog display
to images or text. [&nbsp;<a href="site-catalog.php">More</a>&nbsp;]</span></p>
<p class="text"><strong>CHECKOUT &amp; E-COMMERCE<br>
</strong>Set up options for
  invoices and payment. Available payment types include credit card, check, purchase
  order,
    and PayPal. Credit card numbers
  are sent securely and may be charged manually or automatically through VeriSign&#8482; 
PayFlow Pro (VeriSign&#8482; PayFlow Pro gateway account required.)<span class="text"> [&nbsp;<a href="site-ecom.php">More</a>&nbsp;]</span></p>
